### Delete existing note by ID (happy path, expected 204)
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/notes/{{NOTE_ID}}
Accept: application/json

### Delete note by non-existing ID (expected 404)
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/notes/{{MISSING_NOTE_ID}}
Accept: application/json

### Delete note with invalid ID format (expected 400)
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/notes/not-a-number
Accept: application/json
